This test case demonstrates the search by Primary Key Option of the program
The search by Primary Key is executed with menu option 'p/P'

This test case consists of:
   TC1. Search by Primary Key on Empty Database   =>  Not found
   TC2. Search by Primary Key on Populated Databse => Print Movie Details
   TC3. Search by an incorrect Primary Key on Populated Database = > Not found
